   &UR; NATIONAL _ GENERAL (Moved in ``a'' category) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   HOSPITAL-INTERNS-III (New York) _ The third of four feature
articles on a year in the lives of hospital interns: The interns
struggle to sort out the mixed messages and contradictions of
medical training in the age of managed care. By N.R. Kleinfield.
</P>
