<HEADLINE>
THIS IS A TEST - THIS IS A TEST  
 PLEASE DISREGARD -TEST -TEST 
</HEADLINE>
   Testing, testing.  
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ This is a test from the Hearst bureau.
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
