   _ Product placement: The Berkeley Bark sends proud word that its
``Dog Is My Co-Pilot'' bumper sticker was seen on a refrigerator on
the ``Dharma &AMP; Greg'' show last week.
</P>
<P>
   _ Fox News Channel editors wouldn't let abortion opponent  &UR; Matt &LR; 
 &UR; Drudge &LR;  show a National Enquirer picture of a 21-week-old fetus on
his show on Saturday, so Drudge walked off before airtime.
</P>
<P>
   &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; WHO SAID WHAT &LR;
</P>
<P>
   `` `Sir Sting' doesn't have much of a ring to it. It's going to
have to be Lord Sting or nothing.''
</P>
<P>
   _ Sting, in Rolling Stone, on the possibility of knighthood.
</P>
