<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-16 13:56 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1386 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e BC-AUTHOR-MCFEELY-ART-BO     11-16 1175
