(Eds: Not for use before Thursday, Nov. 18) 
 
 
By BARBARA DE WITT 
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Stylish slippers
</P>
<P>
   According to a recent study by the American Pet Products
Manufacturers, two-thirds of America's pet owners buy gifts for
them, whether it's a catnip mouse, designer collar (Chanel and
Coach have them), or a special bed. If you're leaning to the
latter, check out the soft wool slipper cat bed by English designer
Sheila Parness, priced at $150. It's available in the the Neiman
Marcus By Mail pet catalog, along with other custom beds, plus
jewelry, dishes and leather jackets for your four-legged friends.
To order, call (800) 825-8000. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
Bohemian chic
