<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-16 17:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1597 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e BC-JOYCE-MAYNARD-NYTR &LR;      11-16 1003
