<P>
   INTERNATIONAL
</P>
<P>
   EGYPT-CRASH _ CAIRO _ The reaction and other developments from
Egypt to the latest news about the pilot in the crash of EgyptAir
Flight 990. Developing. (Kaplow, Cox News Service
</P>
<P>
   CLINT0N-OSCE _ ISTANBUL _ With fighting raging between Russian
troops and Chechen rebels several hundred miles from here,
President Clinton will lead his counterparts from the 54-nation
Organization for Security and Cooperation in Europe, OSCE, in their
annual summit. Chechnya appears certain to dominate the forum _ the
civil analog to the NATO military alliance. We set up the summit.
