recent national trend toward putting children on trial as adults, a
state jury convicted a boy here on Tuesday of second-degree murder
in the fatal shooting of a man two years ago. But the jury here in
Oakland County Circuit Court also acquitted the boy, Nathaniel
Abraham, who is 13, of felony possession of a firearm during the
commission of a crime. By Keith Bradsher.
