news of the Mobile-Squelcher, a gizmo that allows users to jam the
cell phones of talkers who are annoying them. The device was
introduced at an electronics fair in Hong Kong and _ if its makers
can get around laws banning telephone jamming _ will be on the
market in Australia in a few months.
</P>
