<HEADLINE>
WHITEFIRE RESURRECTS `ALLEN'S ALLEY' 
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
Our rating:  1 star  
(Eds: Not for use before Friday, Nov. 19) 
(Eds: Fact box at bottom) 
By JULIO MARTINEZ 
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
 
