<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-16 20:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1806 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-FED-MARKETPLACE-820&AMP;A     11-16 1173
