FBN-MONDAY-NIGHT-1, 11-16 -- Al Michaels, the undisputed star, and
Boomer Esiason in the broadcast booth for ABC's ``Monday Night
Football.'' The Foxboro booth is cramped, with hot lights, one
camera looking in and another looking out and cables spread on the
floor like nerve ganglia carrying the game's impulses to America.
(Michelle V. Agins/New York Times Photo)
